<figcaption class="attribution">
        <span class="attribution__caption">Note: This tool assumes the borrower paid on time every month that a payment was made and does not account for late fees. The calculations are based on a simple interest formula that is common in most used car loans but may not reflect the terms of every loan. This tool assumes loan extensions were taken in the first half of the loan term, with the first granted on the sixth month. This calculator provides an estimate. State laws can affect interest charges during an extension. The standard monthly payment may have slight discrepancies depending on how lenders calculate the number of days per month</span>
    
