<div class="lead-in">
            <p class="lead-in__title" id="loans-with-extensions-result-in-inflated-final-payments">Loans With Extensions Result in Inflated Final Payments</p>
                <div class="lead-in__intro">
            <p>The monthly payment for a 72-month, $15,000 loan with a 25% interest rate is $404. But with two extensions early in the loan, the borrower’s final payment will be more than six times higher.</p>

        </div>
    </div>


