    <div class="story-card__description">
                
        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/auto-loan-calculator-with-extensions">
                                    What No One Tells You About Car Loan Deferments
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            When you defer a car payment, you’ll likely end up owing more at the end of your loan. Our free auto loan calculator tool was built to help borrowers figure out their final payment amount and understand how car loan extensions work.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
            by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/byard-duncan">Byard Duncan</a>, <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/ryan-gabrielson">Ryan Gabrielson</a> and <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/lucas-waldron">Lucas Waldron</a>,             <time class="timestamp" datetime="2024-09-12EDT05:05">Sept. 12, 5:05 a.m. EDT</time>
        </p>

            </div>
