                        <a class="story-card__series" href="https://www.propublica.org/series/the-title-pawn-trap">The Title Pawn Trap</a>
        
        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/how-we-measured-title-lending-industry-georgia">
                                    How We Measured the Title Lending Industry in Georgia
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            No statewide agency monitors Georgia’s high-interest title lenders, so we used a variety of data sources to reveal the scope of the industry and its impact on customers who file for bankruptcy.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
            by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/joel-jacobs">Joel Jacobs</a>, ProPublica, and <span class="name">Margaret Coker</span>, <a href="https://thecurrentga.org">The Current</a>,             <time class="timestamp" datetime="2023-07-13EDT04:59">July 13, 2023, 4:59 a.m. EDT</time>
        </p>

                <p class="story-card__unit">Local Reporting Network</p>
            </div>
</div>
                    


        
                    
